item.title: CVE-2021-39314|2024-08-04T02:06:41.796Z -- woocommerce%20enviopack -- woocommerce%20enviopack
item.description: The WooCommerce EnvioPack WordPress plugin is vulnerable to Reflected Cross-Site Scripting via the dataid parameter found in the ~/includes/functions.php file which allows attackers to inject arbitrary web scripts, in versions up to and including 1.2.
